fm: int bitwiseComplement(int n) {              int res = 0, mul = 1;                  if(n == 0)                                                      return 1;                  while(n > 0) {                          int rem = n % 2;             rem ^= 1;                          res += rem * mul;             mul *= 2;                          n = n / 2;         }                  return res;     }

fm: vector<int> nextLargerNodes(ListNode* head) {              vector<int> res;         ListNode* temp = head;                  vector<int> v;                  while(temp != NULL) {             v.push_back(temp->val);             temp = temp->next;         }                  // Now, find the next greater right of all elements of vector v         stack<int> w;                  for(int i=v.size()-1; i>=0; i--) {                          if(w.empty() == true)                                       res.push_back(0);             else if(w.top() > v[i])                                     res.push_back(w.top());             else if(w.top() <= v[i]) {                  while(w.empty() == false && w.top() <= v[i])            w.pop();                                  if(w.empty() == true)                                   res.push_back(0);                 else                                                    res.push_back(w.top());             }                          w.push(v[i]);         }                  reverse(res.begin(), res.end());         return res;     }

fm: vector<vector<int>> levelOrder(TreeNode* root) {              vector<vector<int>> res;                  if(root == NULL)                    return res;                  vector<int> path;         queue<TreeNode*> q;                  q.push(root);                  while(q.empty() == false) {                          int n = q.size();                          // All nodes at one level             for(int i=0; i<n; i++) {                                  TreeNode* temp = q.front();                 q.pop();                                  path.push_back(temp->val);                                  if(temp->left != NULL)           q.push(temp->left);                 if(temp->right != NULL)          q.push(temp->right);             }                          res.push_back(path);             path.clear();         }                           return res;     }

fc: class Solution { public:          int findNumber(vector<int> v) {                  int sum = 0;         int mul = 1;                  int n = v.size();                  for(int i=n-1; i>=0; i--) {             sum += mul * v[i];             mul *= 2;         }                  return sum;     }          void dfs(TreeNode* root, vector<int> path, int &res) {                  if(root == NULL)                            return;                  path.push_back(root->val);                  if(root->left == NULL && root->right == NULL) {                          int t = findNumber(path);             res += t;         }                  dfs(root->left, path, res);         dfs(root->right, path, res);                  path.pop_back();                  return;     }          int sumRootToLeaf(TreeNode* root) {              int res = 0;                  if(root == NULL)                            return res;                  vector<int> path;                  // Find all root to leaf paths                  dfs(root, path, res);                               return res;     }      };
